This code and accompanying dataset site alongside an article written for Medium:

Keeping your data science skills primed, ready and growing
Why setting yourself some random challenges every so often can help your life as a part-time data scientist — an example using Scottish Rugby title winners and animated bar plots…

https://towardsdatascience.com/keeping-your-data-science-skills-primed-ready-and-growing-dc6977a4f32a


For the original article, the Wikipedia page for Premiership championship winner was accessed and scraped 14/10/2018.

